Ecological notes : very common in broad-leaved and carr woodland; also found in mixed woodland and conifer plantation; damp and wet heathland; wetlands including water meadows, fens, reed beds, basin mires and bogs; grazed grassland; former gravel workings; vegetation beside reservoir. iii–x.
